  "title": "(🎉✨Fun Environment!!) Events Customer Service",
  "description": "<p>Events Customer Service Associate (Entry Level)</p><p></p><p>Job Description</p><p>We are looking for customer-oriented individuals to join our Events Customer Service Team. This role involves engaging members of the public at events and roadshows, representing our clients through face-to-face interactions, and supporting sales activities as part of direct marketing campaigns.</p><p><br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>- Engage customers at events and roadshows in a friendly and professional manner</p><p>- Provide product or service information and address general enquiries</p><p>- Carry out direct marketing activities for clients through face-to-face interactions</p><p>- Support and complete on-site sales transactions</p><p>- Work closely with team members to ensure smooth event execution</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>No prior customer service or sales experience required</p><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p><p>Comfortable interacting with members of the public</p><p>Service-oriented mindset with a positive attitude</p><p>Willingness to learn and undergo training</p><p>Able to work in a fast-paced, team-based environment</p><p><br /></p><p>Training & Development:</p><p>Customer service, product, and basic sales training provided</p><p>On-the-job coaching and support from experienced supervisors</p><p>Opportunities to develop customer engagement and communication skills</p>",
